description:
This step-by-step video instruction series will help you understand define and leverage your brand. This is the exact same process I use with all of my clients. The process is simple but it is not easy.

Discovering your brand requires your to take a deep dive look at yourself, maybe for the first time ever. Because of this, it is designed so you can work at your own pace. Some people will get through the materials in a couple of weeks, others may take up to four weeks.

Included with the course are easy to use worksheets that will not only serve to help you document your findings but will also be used to help you put together your brand message.
title: The Personal Branding Blueprint
